node.text: @artisansdegeneve introducing the new series “Meet the Passion” and today met and interviewed John Demsey, Executive Group President of Estee Lauder,  he opens up about his  passion for fine art, customization and watchmaking

Let’s have a closer look on the @wristaficionado Audemars Piguet Royal Oak Double Balance Wheel “High Jewellery” ref 15469BC. A watch that combines the famous octagonal case with the best of gem setting 💎 This watch is the ultimate black-tie watch – time-only and eminently classical in size at just 37 mm. Available at @wristaficionado boutique 🇺🇸

node.text:
Charles LeClerc of Scuderia Ferrari during the F1 Gp Monza qualifications wore his unique Richard Mille RM 67-02 Automatic. This timepiece has been exclusively made for himself using the colors of his country Monaco. The bezel and caseback are in white quartz TPT®, caseband in red Quartz TPT® while the bridges are hand-painted in white and red.
Retail price: Unreleased
•
📸 @richardmille | @vertigo1983

node.text:
Introducing the new Audemars Piguet Royal Oak Perpetual Calendar full titanium ref. 26574TI.
The new dial design pairs a blue “Grande Tapisserie” pattern with contrasting grey subdials, bestowing the model with a contemporary two-tone aesthetic. Initially available only for the US market and from October extended to the whole world. 
⌚️ tag price: $80,000.00
•
📸 @hodinkee @jonbues
